

---

## Scripts Toolbox — Flavor-Specific Notes

### Architecture

Cross-platform script collection. Every tool has both `.sh` and `.ps1` variants.

### Conventions

- Shell scripts: `#!/usr/bin/env bash` + `set -euo pipefail`
- PowerShell: `#Requires -Version 7.0` + `[CmdletBinding()]`
- Shared logic in `.logic` or `.conf` files (DRY principle from git-sutras)
- Non-interactive design — no `read` or `Read-Host` prompts (scripts must work in automation)

### Testing

No automated test framework. CI validates syntax:
- `shellcheck` for `.sh` files
- `python -m py_compile` for `.py` files
- `pwsh` parser check for `.ps1` files
